embeds.description:
1. Do not use the power imbalance you have with these permissions unless necessary (not for jokes).

2. To properly mute someone use the /mute command.

3. Do not touch anyone's self-assignable roles, filter roles, or @member role (UNLESS you are changing their age roles for verification or removing a duplicate).

4. Make sure people don't have more than one DM status or age role (and make sure everyone has at least one).
